title: Bleeders DIEgest Season One Wrap Up Show: Part 2
itunes:title: Bleeders DIEgest Season One Wrap Up Show: Part 2
description:
Join us for the Bleeders DIEgest Season One Wrap Up Show: Part 2. We talk about concept ideas, guest actors, writing and voice acting and so much more on episodes 14-26. You don't want to miss this episode!! If you are new to Bleeders DIEgest be sure to check out episodes 14-26 before listening. Our new season starts January 20th, 2022!  **Join our official Patreon and support the show! Get ad-free episodes, shout-outs, and more. Click the link to join https://www.patreon.com/bleedersdiegest To haunt us on social media click here https://linktr.ee/bleedersdiegest



Hosted on Acast. See acast.com/privacy for more information.
